<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有唔同香味簡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74c086733476d716eed5de2b3b1eeb6d9b9eb4e","tid":187233,"uid":103102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T21:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大壓力 自尋煩惱 燥狂<br />\n食煙好似打咗鎮靜劑 個人會好冷靜地點煙<br />\n想戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食左幾耐？ <br />\n我食左4個月 已經發現好難戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5528585c7cbb1ef6a329f98b5928d6d87329313","tid":187233,"uid":43765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T21:40:35.000Z","msg":"感觸 有日一朝落到樓下好大風 <br />\n望住啲樹隨風擺動就諗起樹欲靜而風不息...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fc19f7baf2b89a29d6e41db63a430caa7d73ec","tid":187233,"uid":87372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T21:44:03.000Z","msg":"失戀去飲酒，朋友比支就食，一食食左3年<br />\n最近半年戒左<br />\n希望大家都快d戒煙"},{"pid":"0b71bc3d2d8fc7242dab923ea869efb0e60d6c02","tid":187233,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T21:47:44.000Z","msg":"大環境 個個都食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後壓力"},{"pid":"659641506558b0c3cf5e0abd11be1256ca915679","tid":187233,"uid":28153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T21:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係，分左手就想食，但覺得好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n捲煙唔臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有唔同香味簡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n捲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfc7dc6b7a03213a61d8c9ac197ca65ee11d39a","tid":187233,"uid":28153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T21:54:28.000Z","msg":"第一支係因為拍拖鬧交好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁就食咗兩年"},{"pid":"c14749e65b91de72f292befb2f38eb478b842c93","tid":187233,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T21:55:03.000Z","msg":"係Marlboro 臭啫"},{"pid":"6ee56c2462f4235c26c4ead791f9173275c7caae","tid":187233,"uid":63107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T22:10:21.000Z","msg":"若你此刻點起煙 你會想起誰"},{"pid":"754accc9469a1f5d9be244b122f88739ee53019d","tid":187233,"uid":75235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T22:11:36.000Z","msg":"翻工好攰 同事又好多都食"},{"pid":"a35cbe817820b5b9ff005173249a99835db76b43","tid":187233,"uid":75235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T22:13:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>翻工好攰 同事又好多都食</blockquote><br />\n都係心癮多 唔好成日諗住就戒到<br />\n食完個心舒服但個肺好唔舒服 所以都係唔好再食啦"},{"pid":"a84795d0fdd2a26fe73cfdd8a6a35b83cfa51377","tid":187233,"uid":51004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T22:20:46.000Z","msg":"正垃圾<br />\n快啲生cancer啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb1690ee88804f7ee5fee33ec36b6c46fae1529","tid":187233,"uid":98848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T22:41:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>若你此刻點起煙 你會想起誰</blockquote><br />\n半支煙勝過殘破的天國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afde3f32dfa943da5ea0463a5a4c9db2906fc500","tid":187233,"uid":59414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T22:50:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>失戀去飲酒，朋友比支就食，一食食左3年<br />\n最近半年戒左<br />\n希望大家都快d戒煙</blockquote><br />\n我第一支煙都係朋友比 <br />\n到依家食左2年"},{"pid":"21574fb89a7d1bff468d15ec9a320fc64d7469d1","tid":187233,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T23:03:32.000Z","msg":"一齊果陣勸佢戒<br />\n分手之後到我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5705872ef145b1fff987f6af94d4b161715a57","tid":187233,"uid":62141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T23:06:14.000Z","msg":"飲醉左&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"603b594ef5691f895347ba5d1bb986ec705eab06","tid":187233,"uid":84620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T23:10:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>失戀去飲酒，朋友比支就食，一食食左3年<br />\n最近半年戒左<br />\n希望大家都快d戒煙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n煙齡同你差唔多 但唔知應該點戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:好想戒"},{"pid":"76d1ee464b8e6136a2b08c55ed4a399b6124719a","tid":187233,"uid":17633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T23:14:12.000Z","msg":"識得揀朋友好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffa64662117878370c2c827396084d02962bfc6","tid":187233,"uid":88182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T23:15:24.000Z","msg":"好味 又有型"},{"pid":"a68ce34ebbb1665d30558d0779057e54fa4fe825","tid":187233,"uid":87372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T23:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>失戀去飲酒，朋友比支就食，一食食左3年<br />\n最近半年戒左<br />\n希望大家都快d戒煙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n煙齡同你差唔多 但唔知應該點戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:好想戒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n心癮好緊要，開頭比較辛苦，我無靠任何東西輔助戒煙<br />\n以前日日一包，一放break，沖去吸返3支先上堂/返工<br />\n巴打加油，有需要搵下戒煙熱線，你應該好快戒到！"},{"pid":"b37e9aabc98ebb3edcbc2989d92ab38387327b62","tid":187233,"uid":7833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T23:30:01.000Z","msg":"脾氣好大好易燥 食支煙既時候好似幫自己cooldown咁<br />\n同埋個心難受既時候食煙好似吐返自己一部分既靈魂出黎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁就食左四年了"},{"pid":"21b283043acb61b91b752054782b664892aa94f4","tid":187233,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:10:41.000Z","msg":"貪玩"},{"pid":"516dd3e8a64ba2d8b189011c54cee79240c5db46","tid":187233,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係Marlboro 臭啫</blockquote><br />\n芝麻味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c57a058542cd722df0920098fd5b417f206d387","tid":187233,"uid":6778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:19:14.000Z","msg":"幾年exp   轉左vape之後覺得煙真係好臭"},{"pid":"2a29279d3eec9b0206c148471a3e9d1a5b3ae364","tid":187233,"uid":37871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:21:55.000Z","msg":"頂....個個都係分手先開始食....<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都係....依家食左兩年幾，心癮居多。<br />\n<br />\n其實我既嗅覺係好敏感的，所以次次係屋企食完，都要洗手加消毒液，如果上床訓，會擦埋身。<br />\n<br />\n街就比較少食，因為冇咁多清潔工具。"},{"pid":"b321b948d013e70793fc17c4d75e6f5afca43bbc","tid":187233,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:28:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26f60b8d8e747bbd7583def297dca9d812c6fd21","tid":187233,"uid":45605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:32:51.000Z","msg":"返工朋友遞左支比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9743a8b6fdac902b0bf29cac00955a3bb59b738","tid":187233,"uid":78312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>翻工好攰 同事又好多都食</blockquote><br />\n都係心癮多 唔好成日諗住就戒到<br />\n食完個心舒服但個肺好唔舒服 所以都係唔好再食啦</blockquote><br />\n成班都食好難唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b58a9c34511d395278bc5c02c94d538165169b","tid":187233,"uid":92690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:13:39.000Z","msg":"好細個好奇偷老豆煙食, 但之後係朋友正式教識我食煙, 食左10幾年<br />\n<br />\n利申:已戒3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6630bdf47a04b17ffd87d77ca3e516ba43cccaa6","tid":187233,"uid":34335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:18:00.000Z","msg":"想知點解啲人咁on9食煙，食完之後覺得啲人真係on9"},{"pid":"b67013bd307e4b361609c9842ac20c05aeb53d60","tid":187233,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:18:40.000Z","msg":"肚餓咪食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8b557af995f493b0aaa3b2e83ca75d6c6c60b2","tid":187233,"uid":40512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:21:18.000Z","msg":"溫書要食煙 <br />\n平時溫四個鐘就頂唔順<br />\n食一支可再啲四個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8dfd95cf51a9799164058004da9fecdf4e5773a","tid":187233,"uid":40512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:21:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>溫書要食煙 <br />\n平時溫四個鐘就頂唔順<br />\n食一支可再<span style=\"color: red;\">頂</span>四個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"870ab15ceab5a8282a548dfc37b5c467565c2340","tid":187233,"uid":26446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:25:00.000Z","msg":"唔食煙既人根本唔知道一枝煙幫到個人幾多<br />\n唔好講話長遠會點會點，遲早都係死架啦<br />\n食左半年 冇後悔過 係我失戀 屋企出事 讀書有壓力既時候 冇左呢啲煙根本捱唔到落去 每個人都有自己減壓方法架啦 有人鍾意打飛機 有人睇書 憑咩食煙就要比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f9a5aedec64b69db4086b23d90abd1fd74acdb","tid":187233,"uid":52342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔食煙既人根本唔知道一枝煙幫到個人幾多<br />\n唔好講話長遠會點會點，遲早都係死架啦<br />\n食左半年 冇後悔過 係我失戀 屋企出事 讀書有壓力既時候 冇左呢啲煙根本捱唔到落去 每個人都有自己減壓方法架啦 有人鍾意打飛機 有人睇書 憑咩食煙就要比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為睇書打丁唔會害人囉<br />\n隨非你帶住個抽油煙機出街食<br />\n如果唔係係你後面行啲人真係多得你唔少<br />\n咁簡單都唔明<br />\n你話食煙禍害幾大"},{"pid":"acc26b753182339207b1c3ad399289fa0f6da44e","tid":187233,"uid":79093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:29:38.000Z","msg":"知道鐘意既人有女朋友 <br />\n佢都知我鐘意佢 我地既關係係友人以上 戀人未滿<br />\n我堅持左又等左佢好耐 成年幾<br />\n<br />\n發現左之後 個人開始失控 好驚眼前呢個人 <br />\n我想走但佢又唔比 其實我都係唔捨得 <br />\n然後就食左第一枝煙 但上唔到癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n唔想身體變差 自己冷靜到都唔食了"},{"pid":"08b1414037f74bf150d3f1a663b4b74f6dccf024","tid":187233,"uid":79093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:30:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔食煙既人根本唔知道一枝煙幫到個人幾多<br />\n唔好講話長遠會點會點，遲早都係死架啦<br />\n食左半年 冇後悔過 係我失戀 屋企出事 讀書有壓力既時候 冇左呢啲煙根本捱唔到落去 每個人都有自己減壓方法架啦 有人鍾意打飛機 有人睇書 憑咩食煙就要比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 我未食個陣都唔鐘意食煙呢件事<br />\n食左枝煙後 就冷靜左落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ddf981762227c78a13fbb11a757042fa35dfab7","tid":187233,"uid":51079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:28:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔食煙既人根本唔知道一枝煙幫到個人幾多<br />\n唔好講話長遠會點會點，遲早都係死架啦<br />\n食左半年 冇後悔過 係我失戀 屋企出事 讀書有壓力既時候 冇左呢啲煙根本捱唔到落去 每個人都有自己減壓方法架啦 有人鍾意打飛機 有人睇書 憑咩食煙就要比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 我未食個陣都唔鐘意食煙呢件事<br />\n食左枝煙後 就冷靜左落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩呀 食完個種 個心俾刀吉 既感覺會暫時消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc39ed9068d75345d88f0ea593e7d6eb6781c902","tid":187233,"uid":89666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:30:20.000Z","msg":"之前番工唔開心 壓力大, 呢排失戀煙駁煙咁食"},{"pid":"3f3d81a765f0f54cfd651afa7dd29ca6c90ecf72","tid":187233,"uid":5803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:33:31.000Z","msg":"見老豆食 自己貪得意買黎食下<br />\n但又可以無上癮 <br />\n而家完全戒左 仲覺得d煙好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d43cc032497f39ee92ef6763581dc3fa0042aa","tid":187233,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"我係咁吸阿爸啲煙都夠晒攞命<br />\n你地仲自己走去食<br />\n未戒煙 記得唔好生仔啊 pk"},{"pid":"f6df1a1fcc4abb15006ceb648ffd34532f85a39e","tid":187233,"uid":38264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:42:09.000Z","msg":"佢教我食煙 然後佢就離開咗我 宜家日日係同佢之前一齊食煙個個位自己食 個心痛到..."},{"pid":"9f06a87d40d066371353b3e87b1821384d4f70b4","tid":187233,"uid":26446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:55:23.000Z","msg":"我控制到自己只要唔係唔開心就唔會食 <br />\n所以我覺得一直我都係利用緊D煙<br />\n食左半年 身邊都唔係太多人知我食煙"},{"pid":"ef8a80cb8e89632240dc7d21d59d66ca70bd7cb1","tid":187233,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:11:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係Marlboro 臭啫</blockquote><br />\n芝麻味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c445cb10d6ffc91625d0437da92fe72069580a","tid":187233,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:12:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我控制到自己只要唔係唔開心就唔會食 <br />\n所以我覺得一直我都係利用緊D煙<br />\n食左半年 身邊都唔係太多人知我食煙</blockquote><br />\n慢慢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}